ğŸ”¸ Python tasks:

    Define rules as dictionaries

    Match log lines against each rule

    Extract key info (IP, username, timestamp)

ğŸ”¹ Phase 4: Alerting Engine (alerter.py)
ğŸ”¸ What you'll learn:

